text: These are the official results of the Women's 800 metres event at the 1993 IAAF World Championships in Stuttgart, Germany. There were a total number of 37 participating athletes, with five qualifying heats and the final held on Tuesday 1993-08-17. ==Doping disqualification== Liliya Nurutdinova (Russia) was disqualified after testing positive for the anabolic steroid stanozolol.Phil Hersh: Dopers, Ex-dopers And `Hmmm' Take Spotlight, Chicago Tribune, 22 August 1993Liliya Nurutdinova, Sports-Reference.com ==Final== {| class="wikitable" style="border-collapse: collapse;
